<collectingRegion box="[1080,1297,834,859]" country="Brazil" name="Minas Gerais" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">Minas Gerais State</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1309,1381,834,859]" name="Brazil" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">Brazil</collectingCountry>
. The name is to be regarded as a noun in apposition.
</paragraph>
